Description: Kraft Bank ASA is a Norway-based independent bank. The Bank offers simple products within lending and deposits and focuses on advisory services and customer assistance. The Bank provides accounts checking, savings deposits, money market, mortgage and term loans services, as well as card facilities and Internet banking, consumer financing and housing loan services. It serves clients in Norway.
